            , was indicted for <rs id="t18110710-56-off334" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18110710-56-off334" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18110710-56-off334" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               feloniously forging and counterfeiting, on the <rs id="t18110710-56-cd335" type="crimeDate">9th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110710-56-off334 t18110710-56-cd335"></join>, a certain order for the payment of 78 l. 17 s. 9 d. with intent to defraud 
                     
                        <persName id="t18110710-56-victim527" type="victimName">
                           Henry 
                           Oppenheim
                        <interp inst="t18110710-56-victim527" type="surname" value="Oppenheim"></interp>
