                        <interp inst="t18110710-56-victim527" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                     
                  
               
                  </rs>.</p>
               <p>SECOND COUNT. - for uttering and publishing as true, a like forged order, with like intention.</p>
               <p>TWO OTHER COUNTS. - for like offences, stating the intention to be to defraud 
               
                  <persName id="t18110710-56-victim529" type="victimName">
                     Isaac 
                     Spooner
                  <interp inst="t18110710-56-victim529" type="surname" value="Spooner"></interp>
